ify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">2.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Daftar Anggota</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">3.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Jurnal</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">1.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Jurnal Umum</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">2.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Buku Besar</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">4.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Inventory</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">1.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Daftar Barang</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 24px;"><span style="font-size:11pt; font-family: 'Arial';color:#000000;display:inline-block;width:16px;margin-left:-16px">2.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Laporan Pembelian</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.50; paddin